cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.HC, cs.MM, cs.SD 

The paper deals with human activity recognition using on-body sensors, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of attributes for recognition is also relevant to human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and multimedia (cs.MM). Additionally, the paper involves deep learning architectures, which is a topic in statistical learning (cs.SD).
